Package: markov.misc
Title: Markov Modeling for Longitudinal Ordinal Outcomes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Johannes", "Schwenke", , "johannes.schwenke@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
    person("Felix", "Herkner", , "felix.herkner@meduniwien.ac.at", role = c("aut", "cph")))
Description: Estimate state occupancy probabilities and treatment contrasts
    for longitudinal ordinal outcomes using discrete-time Markov transition
    models. Supports (partial) proportional-odds model backends from 'VGAM',
    'rms', and 'rmsb'.
